---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="Websites & Apps | AnichLabs OÜ">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Websites & Apps</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Websites, booking systems, WhatsApp automation, and apps for clinics and health-tech.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        Most web and mobile platforms in healthcare are built by general agencies who do not understand clinical workflows, GDPR for health data, or the regulatory shape of medical AI. The result is software that works for a generic small business but breaks down the moment it touches patients, clinical teams, or sensitive data.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-4">
        AnichLabs OÜ builds web and mobile platforms for clinics, health-tech companies, and small operators. From clinic websites with self-hosted booking and WhatsApp automation, to internal data platforms and patient-facing tools. Every project is led by a medical doctor and computer scientist, with GDPR-compliant handling and clinical workflow fit built in from day one.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">What we deliver</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:browser" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Clinic Websites and Booking</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Modern, fast, self-hosted websites with integrated online booking. No monthly licence fees. Multi-professional support, automated confirmations, SEO built in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:whatsapp" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">WhatsApp Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">AI-powered conversational bots integrated with your booking system, with frequently-asked-question handling and clean handoff to humans.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:mobile-android" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Custom Apps and Dashboards</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Patient-facing tools, clinical dashboards, internal data platforms, and operational apps built for the workflows your team actually runs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:lock" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Compliant Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">EU-hosted deployments with data residency, role-based access, audit logging, and consent management designed in from the start.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            We are a small clinic. Do you work at our scale?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Yes. A significant part of our work is with single-location clinics and small operators who need a serious online presence without enterprise overhead. We scope to your size and budget.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Why not just use WordPress or Wix?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">For a basic brochure site, those tools are fine. For booking, WhatsApp automation, GDPR for health data, or any custom workflow, off-the-shelf platforms become expensive, slow, and hard to maintain. We build modern static and headless architectures that are faster, more secure, and cost less to run.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Do you offer ongoing maintenance?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Yes. Every project includes a 12-month warranty for functional issues. Ongoing maintenance, new features, and evolutionary updates are available on retainer or per-engagement.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-16 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Need a serious platform built right?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call to discuss your project and what a proper build looks like for your situation.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>